    <item>
      <title>特朗普检察官敦促对封口费阴谋和掩盖事实定罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/trump-prosecutor-urges-conviction-over-hush-money-plot-cover-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普封口费案的一名检察官敦促纽约陪审团考虑“大量”证据，这些证据表明这位前总统曾试图通过向一名成人电影明星付钱让他对所谓的性接触保持沉默，然后试图掩盖他的踪迹，以影响 2016 年大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/trump-prosecutor-urges-conviction-over-hush-money-plot-cover-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 00:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
