      <title>习近平会见阿拉伯领导人，中国与中东关系超越贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/xi-hosts-arab-leaders-as-china-mideast-ties-widen-beyond-trade</link>
